result.name: Sliverview Seafood Restaurant

reviews.text:
With the beautiful harbour view and garden design, Silver City Restaurant is somewhere you shall not miss. Colourful seafood and veggie dishes satisfy the need for both local gourmets and foodie tourists. 

I have no reservation in recommending this places if you wanna explore the food from this beautiful fisher village.

We had dinner here a few times while visiting family and friends on the island. The food here is just wonderful and price is reasonable. We sat outside the shop front and enjoyed the lively atmosphere with our delicious food. Must try!

Cheap and delicious food at a convenient location, just ten minutes from the pier. Only downside is that the service was a little slow. It's understandable as people in Lantau are very slow paced and have a more laid back lifestyle than in the City.
Expect one old male waiter, all others are suuuper hospitable !👍👍
$41 for a subway set makes it a great place to hang out for a late lunch

result.name: 銀城海鮮酒家

reviews.text:
依间酒家早市做饮茶 午市做客饭 晚市做小菜 咩时间黎食都有会野食 今日就同家人叫左好多小菜

第一碟有佢地出名既炸乳鸽 系用上好传统既四色虾片 

即炸即食 皮脆肉嫩兼肉汁丰富

真心好食! 第二样系鱼香茄子煲 茄子占左煲既7成 好足料

每啖都分布到肉粒同咸鱼粒 送饭一流!

讲到饭 E碟扬州炒饭 起码有10碗加埋既份量 炒至粒粒金黄色 可见每粒饭都占上蛋肉 粒粒分明 好有获气  另外 佢既黄金豆腐系一家要食

外脆内软 每砖都炸到金黄色

粉唔会太厚 每砖豆腐都够硬身 唔会一甲就散 而且面头加上椒盐 十分野味 仲有叫左小炒王,入面有虾干 ,白饭鱼,腰果,韭菜,鱿鱼

白饭鱼炸到好脆 韭菜好甜 虾干都好大条

食到锦上下 饮碗汤先 

入面有肉丝 荀 香菇 同埋CHA烧呀 用料好配合味道 加上胡椒粉 风味更佳

干烧伊面 有超多的面 香浓的蚝油煮面 超好味!

最后 食埋玛拉糕 做甜品 

入面好松软 热辣辣食就最正! 总结:大碟抵食 用料十足 会再光临~

With the beautiful harbour view and garden design, Silver City Restaurant is somewhere you shall not miss. Colourful seafood and veggie dishes satisfy the need for both local gourmets and foodie tourists. 

I have no reservation in recommending this places if you wanna explore the food from this beautiful fisher village.
室内檯櫈很髒，是積了多年灰塵抹了手變黑的髒，地下全是水漬和污漬。室外位置還好，但蚊子多。侍應服務態度愛理不理。食物倒是挺好吃，價錢在梅窩算合理。
出品普通，十一時左右巳经沒有点心叫，顧客大部份是當地居民
